{"tid":2085233,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現朋友另一半係雞竇常客","createTime":"2020-06-29T18:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T09:55:50.000Z","uid":345011,"like":6,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f72d7eb8e6194a5131e37059276db755d4a57c28","tid":2085233,"uid":345011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:20:46.000Z","msg":"借AC<br />\n<br />\n小弟今年23歲<br />\n<br />\n有個中學師妹 畢業後都仲有聯絡<br />\n師妹有個男朋友 佢地一齊左都5-6年<br />\n意外地同一個共同朋友傾偈後發現原來佢男友玩得好癲下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為同佢男友唔係好熟所以之前唔知道<br />\n但係阿師妹成日以為自己男友係100分男友<br />\n仲成日同人講佢男友對佢有幾好...<br />\n<br />\n應該提醒一下佢嗎?<br />\n好似有啲慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2298c77cde044746b0738099cdb8e2128c2d05ea","tid":2085233,"uid":118217,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:22:31.000Z","msg":"分手啦"},{"pid":"dff050f83f39fd5280730b067bffcb15de35a0f5","tid":2085233,"uid":191453,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:24:04.000Z","msg":"有證據就提 冇就講只會比佢覺得你分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab94da6792904c771decc2e3dae39b9d32fe4c38","tid":2085233,"uid":223320,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:29:16.000Z","msg":"暗示就算<br />\n通常呢啲提醒完兩邊不討好 旁人睇又覺得你多事<br />\n你朋友知道嘈完繼續一齊 你就仆街喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申試過 事後好尷尬"},{"pid":"4fe30ac1f0f51ecbe286775f7127648031300c1a","tid":2085233,"uid":55874,"like":4,"dislike":19,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:32:04.000Z","msg":"好老實講 人地過成點關你撚事<br />\n唔好睇得自己咁高覺得自己幫緊人<br />\n唔係人人都鐘意真相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc6e717dd86ea6247f11f5dce5746f0407507dd","tid":2085233,"uid":336524,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy"